Modern music is usually played on these three instruments: { Guitar, electric keyboard}and the {drums.}The guitar is a very common stringed instrument.
{JAZZ} Jazz is a type of American music especialy for dancing,developed from ragtime.The great amount of people use the word Jazz to describe many forms of rhythmic music.It started at the begining of the{19th century.}
Jazz Instruments {Saxophone}:this musical instrument is named after its inventor Adolphe Sax who was born in Belguim in the 18th century.Guitar:this is a stringed instrument ,played by plucking the strings with your fingers.
